{"tid":1495763,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE 仔天下第一","createTime":"2019-08-22T07:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T09:55:09.000Z","uid":186668,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d97d9c9f4fd6e7a8f77592ce64f55c247a621d4","tid":1495763,"uid":186668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"幾年冇見 轉眼間升格埋U <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbfFKtt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbfFKtt.png&h=6736c701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGUSAz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGUSAz9.png&h=57311410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nive_engineering<br />\n【#工程有共鳴 大學新鮮人嘅五大禁忌】<br />\n.<br />\n進入大學校園，意味住準備迎接自由學習嘅年代。各位同學仔會點樣為自己創造獨一無二嘅回憶呢？不過無論點都好，最緊要莫忘初衷，努力讀書、享受大學生活之外，都唔好忘記身邊嘅人呀！<br />\n.<br />\n多姿多采嘅學習生活同埋Hall Life，相信大家都非常嚮往！溫提各位同學仔，我哋IVE工程課程仲有餘額，有興趣嘅就快啲報名喇！<br />\n.<br />\nIVE工程課程餘額申請資料：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2arbUw7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2arbUw7&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=6d8e6bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2arbUw7</a> .<br />\n#IVE工程 #DSE畢業生 #DSE畢業出路 #工程 #高級文憑 #IVEEngineering #IVE招生 #VTC #工程創未來 #smartcity #STEM #JUPAS #大學新鮮人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1YYcKXHGNv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1YYcKXHGNv&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=36065668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1YYcKXHGNv&h=31b318a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1YYcKXHGNv</a>"},{"pid":"b32ff0f0e61d1d218cc03fd2f237a4739e198172","tid":1495763,"uid":121247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"問過恒管未？"},{"pid":"648eedc057c86ccea2e0d4e843588c3f08a32c42","tid":1495763,"uid":220701,"